    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Seasonala Cemetery</i> is a meditative experience that invites players to explore the serene beauty of a living, breathing cemetery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Using your system’s real date and time, the game changes dynamically – visit in the summer to see the cemetery bustling with life, or explore in the quiet, snowy winter. Observe and interact with NPCs and animals as they visit <i>Seasonala Cemetery</i>, all while listening to ambient sounds recorded from a real-life cemetery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Seasonala Cemetery</i> is a peaceful yet poignant reflection on life and death.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >See how the cemetery changes through the seasons, time of day, and weather.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn about the city’s history through its gravestones.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with the animals that call the cemetery home and the people who visit the cemetery at different times of the day, month, and year.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Listen to ambient sounds recorded from a real-life cemetery alongside a beautiful soundtrack composed by halina heron.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up flowers, rocks, pinecones, and more and place them on gravestones you visit.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A completely free experience for Windows and Mac.</p></li></ul>",
